name: [SPOILERS!] FIXED Enoshima Junko Danganronpa
description:
A LoRA of Enoshima Junko from Danganronpa 1. Trained on NAI.

PLEASE DOWNLOAD THE NEW VERSION! The first version was a test version that I accidentally uploaded!

Works with a weight of 0.8-1. See samples for good prompts (especially for hair color, to get her classic hair color add the tags : "blonde hair".)

Works with most of the anime based models.

Last pictures can be a little gory.

I'm planning to do every Danganronpa characters, so tell me who you wants first!

All of my LoRAs will always be free. If you paid for this or an image using this LoRA, you got scamed! If you wants to supports me, feel free to buy me a Ko-Fi.
